{"tid":1890741,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個係街做過既仆街野!!","createTime":"2020-02-21T10:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T18:02:44.000Z","uid":119688,"like":9,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5048e9f897ba392693d74923c32b6f199a0a0304","tid":1890741,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間肚痛<br />\n好彩附近有間酒樓<br />\n廁格得兩格,其中一格封左<br />\n入去打仗之制<br />\n聽到出面條友唔耐煩<br />\n應該一樣係急屎<br />\n肚痛預左有排屙架啦<br />\n條友又嗌又輕輕力打度門<br />\n心諗由你個仆街慢慢等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到我屙清哂準備開門走<br />\n我就專登唔撚沖廁既<br />\n留返成pet屎醬比佢嘆<br />\n我自己都覺得臭<br />\n到我開門推出去轉身走<br />\n聽到條友大聲屌左一聲<br />\n個心勁舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13eca8fd415bbc0663c823e53eb9457c5698f5c2","tid":1890741,"uid":189911,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"1213523a8c10753a7178c188dff5dd1a012bc784","tid":1890741,"uid":119688,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:47:19.000Z","msg":"你地唔洗問:唔驚比人打咩?<br />\n佢郁手咪打返佢囉<br />\n條友夠西我打咩<br />\n我好撚化大隻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302d2390620aacfa839d15288a84adb224ea617b","tid":1890741,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13eca8fd415bbc0663c823e53eb9457c5698f5c2","tid":1890741,"uid":189911,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632a7e161404fcc2ea96d4da0f00b5788db537a","tid":1890741,"uid":100550,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係係街做既仆街事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />